{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxPicker"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents18OUDSCheckboxPickerV","title":"OUDSCheckboxPicker","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false},{"name":"visionOS","introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false,"beta":false}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxPicker","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxPicker","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A picker allowing to expose several checkboxes and select some of them within the others.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each checkbox contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose the choosen values using this “tag”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It has also some configuration elements which will override the one applied to nested ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","type":"reference"},{"text":" (divider, read only and error mode, layout and outlined)","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":